this is the issue i have... the champ i play dont have the ability to carry a game.. they can EASILY win if my team doesn't feed.. but if my team feeds im not on a champ that can fix that.

you really need to be on a champ that can 1v5 if you get fed to "solo" carry regardless of your teammates.

almost any adc can carry

and champ like{{champion:268}} {{champion:131}} {{champion:105}} {{champion:114}} {{champion:55}} {{champion:54}} {{champion:75}} {{champion:11}} {{champion:78}} {{champion:92}} {{champion:58}} {{champion:102}} {{champion:23}} {{champion:5}} {{champion:62}} {{champion:106}} {{champion:157}} {{champion:112}} {{champion:2}} {{champion:86}} {{champion:7}} {{champion:91}} {{champion:24}} 

are all champs that can carry decently well when fed becuase they all either huge busts that can be reset or extremely high damage while being absurdly tanky

i play{{champion:76}} {{champion:99}} {{champion:115}} {{champion:421}} {{champion:53}} 

all of which can make a HUGE impact on the game..  however nid, lux and ziggs can easily be instagibbed if they get caught by ANY sort of cc.. and blitz well is a support so while i can set up kills perfectly i have to have  teammates get them.. and reksai is a good champ but she isnt a champ that can really 1v5 if fed.. 
i can easily turn the tide of a champ if my other lanes dont feed.

but carrying when teammates who feed is near impossible with the champs i play no matter how fed i get.

i actually USED to be able to carry a little bit on {{champion:76}}  when she could lane because she was an absolutely AMAZING split pusher with{{item:3100}}  and{{summoner:12}} .. but since all i can do with her now is jugnle and i cant drop {{summoner:11}}  or{{summoner:4}}  i can never really take {{summoner:12}}

